text:
Koito,
Didn't you say you were going to have French toast today?

Y-yeah... that's right,
But the French toast shop is gone...

Oh... During the renovation,
Most of the food court changed too.

...B-but, it's okay.
This chiffon cake looks delicious too...!

Aha~
Madoka-senpai and I were wandering around together~

Piye...! S-sorry,
I should've contacted you to see where you were...!

No, it's okay.
It's like a maze in here, inside the food court.

It's only novel at first,
You'll get used to it soon.
